OL,9,FThe Pollen Season
OL,11,FRunning from March to the end of
OL,12,FSeptember, the pollen season is split
OL,13,Finto three main categories:
OL,15,FPollen is a very fine powder produced
OL,16,Fby the male parts of trees, flowers,
OL,17,Fgrasses, and weeds to fertilize other
OL,18,Fplants of the same species. Many
OL,19,Fpeople have an adverse immune response
OL,20,Fwhen they breathe in pollen.
