OL,3,CYour Calendar Pollen Forecast
OL,5,FA pollen count is generated by
OL,6,Fmeasuring the number of pollen grains
OL,7,Fin a given volume of air, using a
OL,8,Fpollen trap.
OL,10,FWhat effect does time of day and
OL,11,Fweather have on pollen count?
OL,13,FPollen counts tend to be higher in the
OL,14,Fearly morning and late evening,
OL,15,Falthough they can sometimes be high
OL,16,Fall day long.
OL,18,FIf the grass is damp, the pollen peak
OL,19,Fwill be later in the morning because
OL,20,Fthe water evaporates before the pollen
OL,21,Fis released.
